{
  "stem": "24195.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then the camp was maybe-- it was actually the airfield, the German air force-- Luftwaffe airfield, that was maybe eight or 10 miles from the city-- maybe less.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so the trucks-- we had to board the trucks, and-- Something already happened back then.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Somebody-- we were crowded, they didn't have enough trucks, and they had trailers attached-- one trailer to each truck.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And these were all pickup-- like open, they were open.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were standing up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they didn't have enough, so really enough trucks, so we were kind of crowded.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And somebody fell out of the truck, out of the front part of the truck, and fell right in front of the wheels of the trailer-- because the trailer was, of course, were attached.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the trailer went over.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I think he was either seriously hurt or killed-- I don't really remember, because they took him away.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Yeah, and there was-- just at the beginning, there was an accident, I guess.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know-- I'm not so sure-- I'm not so sure that they didn't care, but I don't think that the driver noticed.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "These were army drivers-- SS drivers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't think they noticed it until they noticed that the trailer bumped or something, you know?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, you don't see this kind of truck too often.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now you see them here, that they have two and three trailers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But this was just a regular truck with a pickup body.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then you had another-- just a trailer-- with a pickup body that he was pulling.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So that was not very good.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That put a really bad damper on the-- on this going there.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
